===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc}} {{term|φώνημα|sc=Grek|tr=phōnēma||sound}}, from {{term|φωνέω|sc=Grek|tr=phōneō||to sound}}, from {{term|φωνή|sc=Grek|tr=phōnē||sound}}.

